#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:3
msgid "Membership / Partnership module"
msgstr "會員 / 合作夥伴模組"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Membership / Partnership module allows for the creation and sale of "
"memberships. Memberships can be sold through both sales orders and "
"subscriptions products so that businesses can organize and interact with "
"customers as members. This allows for:"
msgstr ""
"會員 / 合作夥伴模組允許建立和銷售會員資格。會員資格可透過銷售單和訂閱產品銷售"
"，以便企業能夠將客戶組織為會員並與其互動。這允許："

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:9
msgid "measuring membership activity, inactivity, sign ups, and churn rates"
msgstr "衡量會員活動、不活動、註冊和流失率"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:10
msgid "viewing membership renewals and expirations"
msgstr "檢視會籍更新與到期"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:11
msgid "following up on membership dues and associated payments"
msgstr "跟進會籍費用與相關付款"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:12
msgid ""
"communicating with members, including sending email blasts based on members' "
"current status"
msgstr "與會員溝通，包括根據會員目前狀態傳送電子郵件群發"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:13
msgid "assigning different membership levels to members"
msgstr "為會員指派不同的會籍級別"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:14
msgid "organizing members-only events"
msgstr "組織僅限會員的活動"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:15
msgid ""
"creating membership lists populated with contact info and other details "
"about members."
msgstr "建立填入聯絡人資訊及其他會員詳細資料的會籍清單。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:18
msgid "The Membership / Partnership module vs. the Membership app"
msgstr "會籍 / 合作夥伴模組與會籍應用程式"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:20
msgid ""
"Beginning with 19.0, the **Membership** app has been replaced by the "
"Membership / Partnership module. This module captures all of the "
"functionality of the **Membership** app, but in a module that is better "
"integrated with other essential apps without requiring a specific "
"**Accounting** module. This replacement does not break any existing "
"membership information when upgrading to 19.0."
msgstr ""
"從 19.0 版開始，\\ **會籍**\\ 應用程式已由會籍 / 合作夥伴模組取代。此模組包"
"含\\ **會籍**\\ 應用程式的所有功能，但其模組與其他必要應用程式的整合更好，且"
"不需要特定的\\ **會計**\\ 模組。此替換在升級至 19.0 版時不會破壞任何現有的會"
"籍資訊。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:26
msgid "App integrations with the Membership / Partnership module"
msgstr "應用程式與會籍 / 合作夥伴模組的整合"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:28
msgid ""
"Once activated, the Membership / Partnership module is fully integrated with "
"both the **Sales** and **Subscriptions** apps. The module is also compatible "
"with the **eCommerce** app, allowing customers to purchase memberships "
"through business's websites."
msgstr ""
"啟用後，會籍 / 合作夥伴模組與\\ **銷售**\\ 及\\ **訂閱**\\ 應用程式完全整合。"
"此模組也與\\ **電子商務**\\ 應用程式相容，讓客戶可透過企業網站購買會籍。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:32
msgid ""
"Finally, the Membership / Partnership module is compatible with pricelists "
"both before and after sales. Price rules can be set before memberships are "
"sold and applied after they are active."
msgstr ""
"最後，會籍 / 合作夥伴模組在銷售前後都與價目表相容。價格規則可在會籍銷售前設定"
"，並在會籍啟用後套用。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:36
msgid "Activating the new module"
msgstr "啟用新模組"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/member_partner_module.rst:38
msgid ""
"The Memberships / Partnerships module can be activated within the **CRM** "
"app. To activate the Memberships / Partnerships module, go "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`CRM` section, check the :guilabel:`Membership / Partnership` "
"box to activate the module. The name given to affiliates can also be "
"customized. By default, it is set to `Members`."
msgstr ""
"會籍 / 合作夥伴模組可在\\ **客戶關係**\\ 應用程式中啟用。若要啟用會籍 / 合作"
"夥伴模組，請前往\\ :menuselection:`客戶關係應用程式 --> 配置 --> 設定`。在\\ "
":guilabel:`客戶關係`\\ 區段中，勾選\\ :guilabel:`會籍 / 合作夥伴`\\ 方框以啟"
"用模組。附屬機構的名稱也可自訂。預設為 `Members`。"

