#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/track_leads/lead_distribution_report.rst:124
msgid ""
"Two horizontal sets of fields appear below a line "
"showing :guilabel:`any` :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`of:` option. This "
"setting filters for records that match **any** of the rules contained "
