msgstr ""
"開啟瀏覽器，在搜尋列中輸入印表機的 IP 位址（例如 `https://192.168.1.25`），然"
"後按 `Enter`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/epos_ssc.rst:57
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/hardware_network/epos_ssc.rst:139
