msgid ""
"If the terminal's IP address changes, update it in the :ref:`Odoo POS "
"settings <pos/use/settings>` and request a new self-signed certificate from "
"QFPay."
msgstr ""
"如果終端機的\\ IP\\ 位址變更，請在\\ :ref:`Odoo POS\\ 設定 <pos/use/settings>"
"`\\ 中更新，並向\\ QFPay\\ 要求新的自簽憑證。"

