msgstr ""
"若要在頁面間瀏覽，請按一下\\ :icon:`fa-caret-left`\\ 或\\ :icon:`fa-caret-"
"right`（:guilabel:`插入號`）圖示。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:216
msgid ""
